name: Dr Raihan Karim
description: Dermatologists focus on diseases and conditions of the skin, nails, and hair. They treat conditions such as eczema, skin cancer, acne, and psoriasis.

name: Dr Mathew Tung
description: Ophthalmologists specialize in eye and vision care. They treat diseases and conditions of the eyes and can perform eye surgery.

name: Dr Jarin Siddika
description: gynecologists (GYNs) provide preventive care and disease management for female health conditions

name: Dr Rashedul Karim
description: Cardiologists focus on the cardiovascular system, which includes the heart and blood vessels. They treat many cardiovascular conditions.

name: Dr Ramjan Ali
description: Endocrinologists treat disorders and conditions that affect the endocrine system. This system involves various glands that make and release hormones in the body.

name: Dr Forhad Hossen
description: Gastroenterologists focus on the digestive system. This includes the esophagus, pancreas, stomach, liver, small intestine, colon, and gallbladder.

name: Dr Safiye Ali
description: A nephrologist focuses on kidney care and conditions that affect the kidneys. Nephrologists also have education in kidney transplants and dialysis.They also require training in internal medicine or pediatrics.

name: Dr Redunul Hoque
description: Urologists treat conditions of the urinary tract in both males and females. They also focus on male reproductive health.

name: Dr Resma Sharmin
description: Pulmonologists focus on the organs involved with breathing. These include the lungs and heart.
